WEBVTT

00:00:05.850 --> 00:00:06.950
Sara senpai...

00:00:08.530 --> 00:00:09.530
I'm so sorry...

00:00:15.290 --> 00:00:16.590
I really can't forgive myself.

00:00:20.730 --> 00:00:22.000
If you'll just wake up,

00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:24.200
I'll do whatever you want.

00:00:26.350 --> 00:00:27.950
Fuu has things he wants to tell you too.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:31.970
So please, just wake up.

00:00:43.830 --> 00:00:44.830
Sara senpai...

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:47.280
Senpai, you're awake?

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:48.920
Are you okay?

00:01:08.170 --> 00:01:09.170
Who are you?

00:01:12.710 --> 00:01:13.710
Wait...

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:24.920
Hi.

00:01:27.150 --> 00:01:28.250
We meet again.

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.980
Now it's your turn

00:01:39.670 --> 00:01:41.560
to pass the message to the next person.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.700
"The Boy Next World My Destiny"
(Episode 8)

00:02:43.980 --> 00:02:46.750
Fuu, just stay calm and listen.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:53.760
The doctor said Sara
might have memory loss.

00:02:57.180 --> 00:02:58.180
Is that...

00:02:58.620 --> 00:02:59.620
really all it is?

00:03:00.630 --> 00:03:01.960
What else could it be?

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:08.510
It's not like he went
back to a parallel world.

00:03:28.610 --> 00:03:30.050
Are you feeling any better?

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:33.020
Don't just barge in here.

00:03:34.440 --> 00:03:35.940
It's an invasion of privacy.

00:03:38.530 --> 00:03:39.730
Why would you say that...

00:03:41.030 --> 00:03:41.460
Sara senpai...

00:03:41.461 --> 00:03:45.620
Stop calling me that. It's annoying.

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:49.860
What do you mean?

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:52.900
I'm not OK with...

00:03:57.490 --> 00:03:58.490
Not OK with... Fuu?

00:04:14.580 --> 00:04:15.580
Tears.

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:21.630
I don't like people who cry in front of me.

00:04:23.380 --> 00:04:25.040
Crying doesn't solve anything.

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:28.660
Your name is Fuu, right?

00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:32.700
If you're going to keep
crying, then get out.

00:04:36.190 --> 00:04:37.750
Do you really... not remember anything?

00:04:39.190 --> 00:04:40.470
You're so noisy.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:43.520
I just had a fever and
collapsed. Then I woke up here.

00:04:44.780 --> 00:04:45.780
That's it.

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:55.640
Why is he gone?

00:05:00.950 --> 00:05:01.950
What is it?

00:05:14.490 --> 00:05:15.490
Oh, you're here.

00:05:16.950 --> 00:05:19.300
Sara senpai's... mother?

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.040
Sara.

00:05:22.410 --> 00:05:23.820
You look better than I expected.

00:05:24.640 --> 00:05:26.490
Um... Sara senpai...

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:28.550
He was unconscious until this morning.

00:05:28.740 --> 00:05:30.000
Come in.

00:05:36.290 --> 00:05:40.240
This is your fiancée, Karen Tsuruhisa.

00:05:40.610 --> 00:05:42.770
Surely you remember her?

00:05:44.130 --> 00:05:46.610
It's been a while, Sara.

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:01.800
Let me out.

00:06:02.590 --> 00:06:03.800
I have to find Fuu.

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:05.580
You can't.

00:06:05.810 --> 00:06:07.110
The time isn't right yet.

00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:09.750
The time?

00:06:11.020 --> 00:06:12.106
What the hell does that mean?!

00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:13.420
I need to be by Fuu's side.

00:06:14.250 --> 00:06:15.250
Don't worry.

00:06:15.850 --> 00:06:17.510
Fuu will be fine.

00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:20.300
How could you possibly know that?

00:06:22.990 --> 00:06:23.990
Who knows?

00:06:24.570 --> 00:06:25.740
Stop messing with me.

00:06:26.180 --> 00:06:27.300
Just calm down.

00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:29.630
This isn't just a dream.

00:06:30.860 --> 00:06:32.510
You've already sensed that, haven't you?

00:06:35.140 --> 00:06:36.440
Then where exactly are we?

00:06:38.260 --> 00:06:39.820
That's a difficult question to answer.

00:06:41.780 --> 00:06:43.210
According to the previous Sara,

00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:49.070
this is the gap between space and time.

00:06:49.590 --> 00:06:50.830
The gap between space and time?

00:06:53.200 --> 00:06:54.200
You keep saying

00:06:54.930 --> 00:06:56.426
"the previous Sara." What does that mean?

00:06:56.450 --> 00:06:57.570
Exactly what it sounds like.

00:06:57.890 --> 00:06:59.300
The Sara who was here before you.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.650
There was one before him, too.

00:07:04.010 --> 00:07:07.080
No one knows why we end up here.

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:10.120
The only thing for certain is

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:13.580
that every previous Sara led us to Fuu.

00:07:15.980 --> 00:07:17.100
You've seen it, haven't you?

00:07:18.350 --> 00:07:21.810
My world, and my Fuu.

00:07:32.940 --> 00:07:35.050
Freshman calling senior.

00:07:35.140 --> 00:07:36.870
If you hear me, give me a sign.

00:07:37.980 --> 00:07:39.570
If you want this back,

00:07:39.980 --> 00:07:41.370
you have to guess who I am first.

00:07:42.330 --> 00:07:45.410
That day, in my world,

00:07:47.050 --> 00:07:48.500
I answered that kid.

00:08:12.990 --> 00:08:14.430
The reason I answered

00:08:15.030 --> 00:08:16.950
was because of a dream
I had the night before.

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:22.420
A very long dream.

00:08:25.170 --> 00:08:27.710
In that dream, we didn't
meet until ten years later.

00:08:30.990 --> 00:08:33.000
That was also shown to
me by the previous Sara.

00:08:36.610 --> 00:08:37.610
Do you want to see?

00:08:39.550 --> 00:08:40.550
Wait.

00:08:41.150 --> 00:08:42.180
Good morning.

00:08:43.030 --> 00:08:44.030
Good morning.

00:08:44.130 --> 00:08:46.440
- Morning.
- Morning.

00:08:50.860 --> 00:08:52.020
Excuse me.

00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:55.510
Who gave you permission to enter?

00:08:57.800 --> 00:08:58.800
Huh?

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.490
What's your name?

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.520
I'll have HR issue you a warning letter.

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:10.099
I just wanted to give you the proposal...

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:12.480
Then you should have
filtered the information first.

00:09:13.370 --> 00:09:15.210
Think about what kind of language

00:09:15.460 --> 00:09:17.570
is appropriate when speaking to me.

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:20.670
Every one of us has
a different personality.

00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:24.700
But we all have one thing
in common: we met Fuu.

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:27.250
And it changed our destiny.

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:33.460
Um... I'm from the planning department...

00:09:34.010 --> 00:09:35.570
Could you please take a look at this?

00:09:35.630 --> 00:09:36.810
The Sara in this world

00:09:37.460 --> 00:09:38.660
was very cold to Fuu.

00:09:39.740 --> 00:09:40.950
Until that very moment.

00:09:44.070 --> 00:09:45.770
Treating your subordinates like pawns...!

00:09:48.940 --> 00:09:49.940
Sara!

00:09:50.050 --> 00:09:51.290
Look at me, Sara!

00:09:51.700 --> 00:09:52.800
Sara, stay with me!

00:09:52.890 --> 00:09:53.890
Look at me.

00:09:55.290 --> 00:09:57.510
He said he saw it the
moment he was stabbed.

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:58.720
Sara!

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:00.490
Another world.

00:10:29.940 --> 00:10:31.590
And then, the end of the world.

00:10:39.610 --> 00:10:41.450
The previous Sara showed it to me.

00:10:43.170 --> 00:10:44.470
So this time...

00:10:45.090 --> 00:10:46.720
it's my turn to show you.

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:50.670
And then you'll show the next Sara.

00:10:53.010 --> 00:10:54.010
I'm going...

00:10:55.450 --> 00:10:56.800
to find Fuu.

00:10:57.860 --> 00:10:59.050
It's still too early.

00:11:03.730 --> 00:11:05.040
When can I finally leave?

00:11:07.520 --> 00:11:08.920
Don't be in such a rush.

00:11:11.050 --> 00:11:12.540
You have to wait until the other Sara

00:11:13.420 --> 00:11:15.360
returns to his original world.

00:11:18.000 --> 00:11:20.960
Just like when you first entered my body.

00:11:35.760 --> 00:11:36.870
Good work today.

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:45.910
I knew it... something still feels wrong.

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:48.290
It's not just his memory.

00:11:48.900 --> 00:11:51.030
He's like a completely different person.

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:53.590
The way he acts with his mother

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:55.290
and his fiancée is so casual.

00:12:00.010 --> 00:12:01.410
What should I do?

00:12:02.150 --> 00:12:03.390
Should I tell him we're dating?

00:12:05.620 --> 00:12:08.080
But he's not the Sara senpai I know.

00:12:12.550 --> 00:12:14.280
I should have just been honest with him.

00:12:16.340 --> 00:12:18.500
It's my fault for being
stubborn and pushing him away.

00:13:36.580 --> 00:13:37.810
Sara senpai...

00:13:59.400 --> 00:14:00.400
Fuu...

00:14:04.150 --> 00:14:06.950
Hey, Sara, have you lost your mind?

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:10.130
I'm perfectly fine.

00:14:10.900 --> 00:14:11.900
Like hell you are.

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:16.240
What did I even do?

00:14:17.260 --> 00:14:19.010
I'm talking about your fiancée.

00:14:19.500 --> 00:14:21.780
Are you really going to let
that devil control your life?

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:24.060
She's not controlling me.

00:14:24.640 --> 00:14:26.280
This was already decided a long time ago.

00:14:28.140 --> 00:14:30.070
You've got to be kidding me.

00:14:30.800 --> 00:14:31.800
So what?

00:14:32.400 --> 00:14:34.410
Did you really tell Fuu
he's not your boyfriend?

00:14:37.730 --> 00:14:38.730
Fuu...?

00:14:41.810 --> 00:14:43.540
Your own boyfriend!

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:46.029
You were so obsessed
with him, always by his side.

00:14:46.030 --> 00:14:47.820
Everyone knew, except maybe you.

00:14:48.330 --> 00:14:52.070
That's why that devil rushed to call
your fiancée back from abroad, isn't it?

00:14:53.510 --> 00:14:55.930
Karen was by my side long before you were.

00:14:56.940 --> 00:14:59.400
It was an arranged marriage
from birth. You know that.

00:14:59.470 --> 00:15:00.660
Of course I know.

00:15:01.180 --> 00:15:03.340
She's always been incredibly possessive.

00:15:03.550 --> 00:15:05.490
Just like a certain someone.

00:15:06.690 --> 00:15:08.290
But you said you were going to fight it.

00:15:09.150 --> 00:15:11.520
Man, we actually believed in you.

00:15:12.480 --> 00:15:14.320
What about Fuu's feelings?

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:18.200
I don't know anyone named Fuu.

00:15:19.770 --> 00:15:21.010
He's a complete stranger to me.

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:24.180
I can't even talk to you.

00:15:25.150 --> 00:15:26.150
Forget it.

00:15:36.980 --> 00:15:38.080
Sara.

00:15:38.130 --> 00:15:39.820
You really need to

00:15:40.020 --> 00:15:41.420
re-evaluate your choice in friends.

00:15:42.190 --> 00:15:43.860
What are you doing eavesdropping?

00:15:45.020 --> 00:15:47.150
I'm your fiancée.

00:15:47.450 --> 00:15:49.580
It's only natural for me to visit you.

00:15:50.100 --> 00:15:51.100
Is that so?

00:15:51.610 --> 00:15:53.330
Well, you're an eyesore. You can leave now.

00:15:54.590 --> 00:15:56.410
If you keep being this rude,

00:15:56.460 --> 00:15:58.640
I'll have to tell your mother.

00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:01.630
Go ahead and tattle all you want.

00:16:03.130 --> 00:16:04.490
While you're at it, tell her this:

00:16:05.200 --> 00:16:07.500
Thanks for giving me
such an annoying fiancée.

00:16:11.990 --> 00:16:13.320
Honestly, Sara...

00:16:13.360 --> 00:16:16.380
Why did you have to break
down at a time like this?

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:19.120
Ah...

00:16:19.900 --> 00:16:20.900
You...

00:16:23.890 --> 00:16:25.880
It's my friend's fault.

00:16:26.490 --> 00:16:27.790
How is Fuu doing?

00:16:29.890 --> 00:16:30.610
Oh...

00:16:30.690 --> 00:16:31.690
Well...

00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:33.200
He's pretty devastated.

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:34.880
I bet...

00:16:35.330 --> 00:16:37.080
My friend really messed up.

00:16:37.610 --> 00:16:39.130
But please don't misunderstand Sara...

00:16:39.890 --> 00:16:41.410
Is there more to the story?

00:16:42.410 --> 00:16:43.659
Since it's a brain issue,

00:16:43.660 --> 00:16:45.060
we have to leave it to the doctors.

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:47.090
Luckily, he has a very capable specialist.

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:49.730
Thank you.

00:16:50.870 --> 00:16:52.090
Why are you thanking me?

00:16:55.780 --> 00:16:57.000
Because you're on Fuu's side.

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:13.200
Ah...

00:17:13.430 --> 00:17:15.100
Taiga... about that kiss...

00:17:15.590 --> 00:17:16.590
Just forget it.

00:17:16.860 --> 00:17:18.800
Calm down... don't let it get to you.

00:17:19.470 --> 00:17:20.470
Deep breaths.

00:17:20.800 --> 00:17:21.800
Senpai...?

00:17:23.800 --> 00:17:25.840
Well... I'll be going then.

00:17:29.150 --> 00:17:30.570
Ugh, damn it.

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:34.860
Why is my heart racing like this?

00:17:50.520 --> 00:17:51.520
Sara senpai...

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:02.440
You've got some nerve
walking around like that.

00:18:07.350 --> 00:18:08.770
I'm just walking.

00:18:09.200 --> 00:18:10.520
Is there a problem?

00:18:11.300 --> 00:18:12.510
How shameless.

00:18:14.250 --> 00:18:15.890
I heard from Sara's mother.

00:18:16.680 --> 00:18:18.370
She said you've been trying to seduce him.

00:18:20.210 --> 00:18:22.320
I don't know what you're planning,

00:18:22.870 --> 00:18:24.750
but Sara likes women.

00:18:26.320 --> 00:18:28.730
He'd never be interested
in you in a million years.

00:18:32.140 --> 00:18:33.140
Then...

00:18:34.030 --> 00:18:35.030
what about you?

00:18:38.470 --> 00:18:39.470
What did you say?

00:18:40.300 --> 00:18:42.639
Are you saying the only reason

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:44.200
he chose you is because you're a woman?

00:18:46.330 --> 00:18:47.640
I...

00:18:50.310 --> 00:18:52.680
I've been special to Sara
since before we were born.

00:19:03.980 --> 00:19:05.390
If you look down on me so much,

00:19:05.460 --> 00:19:06.940
then why did you come looking for me?

00:19:07.480 --> 00:19:08.480
I came to make sure

00:19:09.450 --> 00:19:11.600
you know exactly who his fiancée is.

00:19:13.270 --> 00:19:14.420
His future wife.

00:19:14.910 --> 00:19:16.640
The woman chosen by the Kogami family.

00:19:17.800 --> 00:19:19.510
He belongs to me.

00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:22.980
A commoner like you should stay away.

00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:28.020
Did he turn you down or something?

00:19:30.220 --> 00:19:31.220
What?

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:34.280
Because the current Sara
senpai is pretty cold, isn't he?

00:19:35.300 --> 00:19:37.670
If he'd shown you even a shred of kindness,

00:19:37.940 --> 00:19:39.460
you wouldn't have come looking for me.

00:19:40.300 --> 00:19:41.630
You need to be taught a lesson.

00:19:47.000 --> 00:19:48.680
You're an eyesore no matter where you are.

00:19:49.430 --> 00:19:50.790
I guess that's a talent in itself.

00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:57.740
Now disappear.

00:20:02.510 --> 00:20:03.510
You'll regret this.

00:20:13.700 --> 00:20:14.700
Sara senpai.

00:20:17.430 --> 00:20:18.430
Thank you.

00:20:19.510 --> 00:20:21.069
But shouldn't you be
resting in the hospital?

00:20:21.070 --> 00:20:22.070
That place...

00:20:22.840 --> 00:20:25.020
I couldn't stay there forever,
so I just bailed.

00:20:26.090 --> 00:20:28.370
The doctor looked like he
couldn't wait to get rid of me.

00:20:29.610 --> 00:20:30.970
It just put me in a worse mood.

00:20:36.100 --> 00:20:38.530
So you're... Fuu?

00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:40.840
Yes.

00:20:40.841 --> 00:20:42.040
I'm Fuu Yotsuba.

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:46.740
I'm Sara Kogami.

00:20:48.430 --> 00:20:49.530
I know.

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:55.810
Everyone says you're my boyfriend.

00:20:59.710 --> 00:21:01.520
But I don't remember.

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:04.560
I remember my family and friends.

00:21:05.010 --> 00:21:06.830
I even remember stock market fluctuations.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:09.040
But you...

00:21:09.290 --> 00:21:11.250
I have no memory of you
or anyone related to you.

00:21:20.870 --> 00:21:21.870
I'm sorry.

00:21:42.230 --> 00:21:43.290
It's okay. I understand.

00:21:49.140 --> 00:21:51.990
How... did we meet?

00:21:53.660 --> 00:21:55.100
I was your junior in high school.

00:21:55.530 --> 00:21:57.450
Now I'm a sophomore in
the Education Department.

00:21:58.140 --> 00:22:00.610
Our cafeteria food is actually really good.

00:22:01.300 --> 00:22:03.800
Especially the ramen,
udon, and ginger pork.

00:22:04.830 --> 00:22:05.830
And also...

00:22:05.831 --> 00:22:08.650
That legendary, super-rare
special curry bread.

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:12.050
And... oh.

00:22:12.790 --> 00:22:14.850
You remember everything except me, right?

00:22:19.630 --> 00:22:20.630
Yeah.

00:22:22.050 --> 00:22:24.840
But that's the first I've heard

00:22:25.330 --> 00:22:26.650
about any special curry bread.

00:22:29.370 --> 00:22:31.320
It's my favorite thing to eat.

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:39.020
I see.

00:22:41.380 --> 00:22:42.930
What else have I forgotten?

00:22:46.800 --> 00:22:47.800
Parallel worlds.

00:22:52.590 --> 00:22:53.590
Sara senpai,

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:56.190
do you believe in parallel worlds?

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:03.440
That's ridiculous.

00:23:06.570 --> 00:23:07.960
Then there's no point.

00:23:08.410 --> 00:23:09.510
It's over.

00:23:10.070 --> 00:23:11.930
This Sara senpai is different from him.

00:23:16.410 --> 00:23:17.690
Please, just leave me alone.

00:23:43.790 --> 00:23:44.890
Sara senpai.

00:23:55.150 --> 00:23:56.150
I miss you so much.

00:24:02.050 --> 00:24:04.710
If only I could turn back time...

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:23.640
Because I love you.

00:24:26.100 --> 00:24:27.160
Please come back...

00:24:34.730 --> 00:24:36.590
I don't want to lose you, Sara senpai.

00:25:02.080 --> 00:25:03.710
I haven't even done anything for you...

00:25:05.140 --> 00:25:06.360
I don't need anything.

00:25:07.420 --> 00:25:08.540
Just let me be by your side.

00:26:56.850 --> 00:26:57.850
Sara senpai.

00:26:59.250 --> 00:27:01.306
I was worried because you
haven't left the house in days.

00:27:01.330 --> 00:27:03.590
No, I don't come here
every day, it's just...

00:27:04.700 --> 00:27:06.570
Taiga senpai asked
me to deliver this to you.

